If you prefer the implementation based on Apache JSP 2.1 EL, you have to specify the org.zkoss.xel.el21.ApacheELFactory class. If the Web server doesn't support Apache JSP 2.1 EL, you have to copy el-api.jar (JSP 2.1 API

Required only if you are using the Web server that supports only JSP 2.0.
) and jasper-el.jar (Apache's implementation) to your Web application.
